title: Khum Sab Lum Kong
overview: Archeologist Phetai has always dreamed of herself in traditional clothing and meeting a fatal end. When asked to analyze an artifact that turns out to be fake, she meets Songhop, who resembles her dream killer, sparking instant animosity. Despite their mutual dislike, fate repeatedly pulls them together, linking them to the legend of "Nak Usa," a land guarded by the Four Serpent Clans.
